Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,12,,片名：野 战 排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天 那是我想的东西吗\N{\rEng}Oh, man! Is that what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 新兵 欢迎来到越南 跟我来\N{\rEng}All right, cheesedicks. Welcome to the Nam. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 是菜鸟\N{\rEng}I'll be dipped in shit. New meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们会很喜欢越南的 永远的\N{\rEng}You dudes gonna love the Nam. For-fucking-ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,365天\N{\rEng}365 and a wake-up. Oh, lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:42.18,Default,,0,0,10,,1967年9月B连第25队步兵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:45.18,Default,,0,0,10,,在柬埔寨边境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,下面小心\N{\rEng}Watch it below!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,莫尔豪 走快点\N{\rEng}Morehouse, drop back to slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,查理 谁在队尾\N{\rEng}Who's on tail-end Charlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 这是六队 位置如下…\N{\rEng}Eagle, Eagle, Ripper Six. Pos rep follows.;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,L A W A F…\N{\rEng}Lemur, Alpha, Whiskey, Alpha, Foxtrot....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,华伦 你去队侧\N{\rEng}Warren, you get out on flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,霍梅斯特 什么事\N{\rEng}-Hey, Hoffmeister! -Yo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有香烟吗\N{\rEng}You got a smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 没关系\N{\rEng}-No, man, I don't. -Sin loi, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,B26 为何延迟了\N{\rEng}Bravo 2-6. What's the delay on point?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,又找不到路了吗\N{\rEng}Having compass trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\rEng}Get a move on, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在等什么\N{\rEng}Boy, what you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会咬你\N{\rEng}He ain't gonna bite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是越南兵 死了\N{\rEng}That's a good gook. Good and dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵 新兵\N{\rEng}-Cherry. -Yo, cherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 第六队说我们挡住了他们 完毕\N{\rEng}Move it out. Six says we're jamming them up back there. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他去见鬼吧\N{\rEng}Tell that dipshit to get fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是第25队 听好 我们很快便出发 完毕\N{\rEng}This is 2-5. Be advised. We're moving out shortly. Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你怎么了\N{\rEng}What's the matter with you, Taylor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个大混蛋\N{\rEng}You are one simple son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 对不起\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.99,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,叫另外那个新兵过来 嘉勒 还有军医\N{\rEng}Get that other cherry up here. Gardner. And the doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 军医 上前来\N{\rEng}Gardner, doc, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 军医 上前来\N{\rEng}Gardner, doc, to the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 快过来 你他妈的\N{\rEng}Gardner, get your ass up the hill, you fat fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大胖子 快点\N{\rEng}Hurry up, bubble-butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有事 蚂蚁\N{\rEng}-You all right? -Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我脖子全都是蚂蚁\N{\rEng}I got ants all over my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是红蚂蚁\N{\rEng}You got some red ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,红蚂蚁是杀手 黑蚂蚁最可怕\N{\rEng}Reds are killers. Black ants are the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 混球\N{\rEng}Hurry up, lard-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我很累\N{\rEng}I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,只喝一点\N{\rEng}Just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喝太多 你不要再喝了\N{\rEng}Don't drink too much. I don't want you drinking any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想你抽搐\N{\rEng}I don't want you cramping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你带着太多东西\N{\rEng}You're humping too much stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有一半是不需要的\N{\rEng}You don't need half this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你拿\N{\rEng}I'll haul it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但请你下次先向我请示\N{\rEng}But next time check with me first, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 中士\N{\rEng}Thanks, sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有事吧 没事\N{\rEng}-Are you okay? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是总部 有直升机接近你们\N{\rEng}2-2, this is six. I understand you have a bird inbound at your pos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 请留意\N{\rEng}Bravo Six, be advised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,军资直升机正驶来\N{\rEng}Resupply helo is inbound at this time. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,快点搬军火下来\N{\rEng}Go, you people! Get that ammo off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个字不是这样写的\N{\rEng}It ain't D-E-R-E. It's D-E-A-R.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,而且莎拉也不是那样写的 笨蛋\N{\rEng}And Sarah ain't got no two R's, King. Damn, you dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 她会明白我的意思\N{\rEng}Don't matter. She know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她也不大认识字\N{\rEng}She don't read too good nohow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 又是猪肉\N{\rEng}Look at this shit! Pork again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你换你的火鸡 我不能再吃这玩意了\N{\rEng}Trade me that turkey loaf for this pork shit, man. I can't eat this shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你抽了什么\N{\rEng}What you been smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你不用洗衣服 你要运动一下\N{\rEng}I hope you don't get that laundry gig. Your ass need to hump, hump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,白小子 你在等什么\N{\rEng}Hey, white boy! What you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那个洞不会自己出现的\N{\rEng}That hole won't dig itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,快点挖\N{\rEng}Come on. Get your dick skin on that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,时间无多 快点挖…\N{\rEng}You ain't got all day! Dig, dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有人写过 地狱是不可理喻的\N{\rEng}Somebody once wrote, ""Hell is the impossibility of reason. ""
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方就像地狱\N{\rEng}That"s what this place feels like.; hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来了一周 但已经讨厌这里\N{\rEng}I hate it already, and it"s only been a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 这一周很痛苦\N{\rEng}Some goddamn week, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,最辛苦的事 就是这星期站岗三次\N{\rEng}The hardest thing I"ve ever done is go on point three times this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我在做什么\N{\rEng}I don"t know what I"m doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我连越共在我面前出现也不知道\N{\rEng}A gook could be right in front of me and I wouldn"t know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在很累\N{\rEng}I"m so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早上五点起床…\N{\rEng}We get up at 5.;00 a.m...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,整天走动 四五点钟扎营 挖壕沟 进食…\N{\rEng}...hump all day, camp around 4 or 5, dig a foxhole, eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然后整晚埋伏 或是当哨兵\N{\rEng}... then put out an all-night ambush or a listening post.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新来的 没有人教我任何事\N{\rEng}Nobody tells me how to do anything because I"m new.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没人理会新兵 他们连你的名字也不想知道\N{\rEng}Nobody cares about the new guys. They don"t want to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵的生命不重要 因他没有经验\N{\rEng}A new guy"s life isn"t worth much because he hasn"t put his time in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,若在越南战死 最好在最初几周\N{\rEng}If you"re gonna get killed in Nam, it"s better to get it in the first weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原因是你不会受太多苦\N{\rEng}The logic being, you don"t suffer that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果幸运 留在外围防线…\N{\rEng}If you"re lucky, you stay in the perimeter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,守卫时能够睡三至四小时\N{\rEng}... then pull a guard shift, so you sleep three or four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能真的入睡\N{\rEng}But you don"t really sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我撑不到一年\N{\rEng}I don"t think I can keep this up for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不应该来这里\N{\rEng}I"ve made a big mistake coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多活动\N{\rEng}We got beaucoup movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,第三部队在15公里外被袭击\N{\rEng}3rd Battalion got hit 1 5 klicks north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,越共在树上挂上地雷\N{\rEng}Charlie had claymores strung in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,整排军队被炸 真倒霉\N{\rEng}Blew a whole fucking platoon to pieces. Bad shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,两个中尉和一个上尉被炸死\N{\rEng}Got two lieutenants and a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你想谁去埋伏\N{\rEng}All right, who do you want on ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 你带你的小队出去\N{\rEng}Elias, you take your squad out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,华伦 留下 我需要德斯和乔利亚\N{\rEng}Warren, stay in, but I need Tex and Junior from your squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.55,0:12:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,收到\N{\rEng}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,调动到20M的位置\N{\rEng}Move out in 2-0 mikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为今晚轮到奥尼尔\N{\rEng}I thought it was O'Neill's turn tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,特斯和莫尔豪经验不足\N{\rEng}Tubbs and Morehouse are short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,丰山明天放假 还要他们去吗\N{\rEng}Fu Sheng is going on R and R tomorrow. You want to send them out on ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带新兵去\N{\rEng}You got the fresh meat, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都不懂 可能会遇到事情 仔细想想\N{\rEng}They don't know shit and we'll probably run into something. Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 你想我怎样做\N{\rEng}Great. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我为了一个混蛋要好好睡觉 而让手下被杀吗\N{\rEng}Get one of my guys zapped so a lame ass can get his beauty sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔…\N{\rEng}Hey, O'Neill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,别再罗嗦\N{\rEng}...take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用每天都这么讨厌\N{\rEng}You needn't be a prick every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 叫手下准备好\N{\rEng}Elias, get your men ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他来了三年 以为自己是耶稣\N{\rEng}Guy's in 3 years, thinks he's Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.19,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔 他们留下 但你要去\N{\rEng}O'Neill, your short-timers stay in, but you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要有经验的老兵\N{\rEng}I need veterans out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士\N{\rEng}Sergeant Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们面前应该由我下命令\N{\rEng}I think in front of the men, I need to give the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看来会下雨\N{\rEng}Shit, looks like rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们整晚都要在雨中了\N{\rEng}It's gonna piss on us all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,会令你脸烂掉\N{\rEng}It'll put a serious case of crotch rot on that ugly face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你为那个白人而冒险\N{\rEng}Goddamn, man. You break your ass for the white man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是没有公义的\N{\rEng}No justice around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔又触怒中尉了吗\N{\rEng}What's O'Neill got, a nose up the lieutenant's ass already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么总是我们负责埋伏呢\N{\rEng}Why do we always get fucking ambush?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是因为他们在玩政治\N{\rEng}Because it's politics, man. Politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我有否给你看过露丝的照片 没有\N{\rEng}-Did I show you a picture of Lucy Jean? -No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她会是我的另一半\N{\rEng}She's the one for me all right, that Lucy Jean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她也在等我\N{\rEng}She's waiting for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她很漂亮 你很幸福\N{\rEng}She's real pretty. You're a Iucky guy, Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你有你女朋友的照片吗\N{\rEng}You got a picture of your girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们有一个被 留在家乡的可怜女孩 不是吗\N{\rEng}That leaves some unIucky girl back home, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去\N{\rEng}Tuck this in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,装进去\N{\rEng}Shit-can this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要这个 转身\N{\rEng}Don't need this. Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯 跟乔利亚和泰勒一队\N{\rEng}Tex! You got Junior and Taylor here on your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 不要乱来\N{\rEng}Elias, don't mess with my pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我今晚不是去喝酒 别烦我\N{\rEng}I ain't getting greased tonight. Keep this cheesedick off my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有泰勒\N{\rEng}You got Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 你和我一组\N{\rEng}Gardner, you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你迷路或和队友分开了\N{\rEng}In case anything happens to you, you get lost or separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,千万不要大叫 知道吗 知道\N{\rEng}-...don't yell out, okay? -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要到处走 我们会来找你 好\N{\rEng}-Just sit tight and we'll get to you. -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,准备出发 小心谨慎\N{\rEng}Saddle up! Lock and load!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爸妈不想我来这里\N{\rEng}Mom and Dad didn"t want me to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想我以他们为榜样\N{\rEng}They want me to be just like them.;
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,受人尊敬 工作勤劳 拥有家庭\N{\rEng}Respectable, hard-working, a little house, a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 他们快把我逼疯 你知道妈妈的\N{\rEng}They drove me crazy with their goddamn world, Grandma. You know Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我一向都备受保护…\N{\rEng}Having always been sheltered and special...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想像其他无名氏一样\N{\rEng}...I want to be anonymous like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为国家效力\N{\rEng}Do my share for my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就像祖父在一次大战时一样 和爸爸在二次大战时一样\N{\rEng}Live up to what Grandpa did in the first war, Dad in the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在的确是无名氏了\N{\rEng}Well, here I am. Anonymous, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,和没人在乎的一班人一起\N{\rEng}With guys nobody really cares about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来自荒芜的地方\N{\rEng}They come from the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没听过的小镇\N{\rEng}Small towns you never heard of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,田纳西波兰斯基 密西西比布兰登\N{\rEng}Polaski, Tennessee. Brandon, Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,犹他州波切本 宾夕凡尼亚的旺普\N{\rEng}Pork Bend, Utah. Wampum, Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只念过两年高中\N{\rEng}Two years high school"s about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,若他们幸运 会在工厂找到工作\N{\rEng}If they"re lucky, a job waiting for them in a factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他们大部分都一无所有\N{\rEng}Most of them got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们穷苦而且不受欢迎\N{\rEng}They"re poor and unwanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们却为我们的 社会和自由而战\N{\rEng}...yet they"re fighting for our society and freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 他们知道自己是最底层的人\N{\rEng}It"s weird. They"re the bottom of the barrel, and they know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们自称平凡人\N{\rEng}Maybe that"s why they call themselves grunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为平凡人什么都能承受\N{\rEng}Because a grunt can take it, can take anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我见过最有真本性的人 祖母\N{\rEng}They"re the best I"ve ever seen, Grandma. The heart and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒\N{\rEng}Hey, Taylor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵 轮到你\N{\rEng}Hey, cheesedick, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 轮到你\N{\rEng}-What? -You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定懂得用杀伤地雷吗 我肯定\N{\rEng}-Sure you can work the claymores? -I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓和撞击三次\N{\rEng}Flick the safety off and bang on it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,三次 我知道了\N{\rEng}Three times. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要睡着 否则我不会放过你 知道吗\N{\rEng}Don't catch any Z's on me, or I'll sling your sorry ass! Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我终于在泥泞里找到答案\N{\rEng}Maybe I finally found it way down here in the mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,或许我可以从这里重新来过\N{\rEng}Maybe from down here I can start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以骄傲的做个 堂堂正正的虚假人\N{\rEng}Be something I can be proud of without faking it. Be a fake human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我或许能看见我还没看到的东西 学一些我还没学到的东西\N{\rEng}Maybe I can see something I don"t yet see, learn something I don"t yet know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你 很想你\N{\rEng}I miss you. I miss you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈我想念她 柯里斯上\N{\rEng}Tell Mom I miss her too. Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,乔利亚\N{\rEng}Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 混蛋 轮到你\N{\rEng}-All right, motherfucker. -It's your shift, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去\N{\rEng}Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,引爆地雷\N{\rEng}Blow the fucking claymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓\N{\rEng}Take the safety off! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓\N{\rEng}Take the safety off! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,拉下安全栓 妈的\N{\rEng}Get the safety off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,救我 乔利亚 到这里来救我\N{\rEng}Feed me, Junior! Get over here and feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 冷静下来\N{\rEng}-Jesus-fucking-Christ! -Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 嘉勒被打中 我快过来\N{\rEng}-Doc, Gardner's hit! -Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.08,0:22:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我被击中\N{\rEng}Oh, shit. I'm hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 泰勒被击中\N{\rEng}Doc, Taylor's hit! Taylor's hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 军医\N{\rEng}-Oh, shit. -Doc, doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,伤势怎么样\N{\rEng}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有引爆地雷\N{\rEng}He didn't blow his claymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 只是擦伤 按着\N{\rEng}Relax, man. It's a scratch. Hold this on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要骗我 伤势怎么样\N{\rEng}Don't lie. How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他让他们进入 他当值时睡着\N{\rEng}He let them walk right up on us! He was asleep on his shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大哈洛 留意着他\N{\rEng}Big Harold, keep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.54,0:22:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让他休克\N{\rEng}Don't let him go into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,住口\N{\rEng}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,住口 忍住痛 忍住痛\N{\rEng}Shut up and take the pain. Take the pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,总部 这是六队 我们被袭击 完毕\N{\rEng}Red rag, red rag, bravo six. I have NDPs at this time. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子 你会没事的\N{\rEng}Hey, little guy, you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\rEng}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否知道你会不会死\N{\rEng}Do you know if you're gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你感到一切都没事吗\N{\rEng}Do you feel it'll all be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,胡说 你会离开这里\N{\rEng}No morbid bullshit. You're about to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会给你一日三餐 白床单\N{\rEng}They're gonna give you three hot meals a day. White sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的白人护士拿了你的钱 会给你性服务\N{\rEng}Pretty white nurses will give you blow jobs if you pay them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说过她 不要哄他\N{\rEng}-I heard about them white bitches. -Don't baby talk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个混蛋睡着了 他让他们进来\N{\rEng}The cocksucker fell asleep. He let them walk right up on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,乔利亚 住口\N{\rEng}Just shut up, Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 好吗\N{\rEng}You relax. Okay, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡不是…\N{\rEng}It's not so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那么糟\N{\rEng}...dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\rEng}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.06,0:23:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,多久\N{\rEng}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.86,0:24:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,直升机快来了 撑着点 你会支持着的\N{\rEng}Bird's on the way. Hang in there. You'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉勒 支持着 撑着点 你会没事的\N{\rEng}Come on, Gardner, hang in there. You're gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.98,0:24:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 不要放弃\N{\rEng}Come on. Don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样 嘉勒 不要放弃\N{\rEng}Come on, Gardner, help me. Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:25:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们好好看看这个狗屎\N{\rEng}You all take a good look at this Iump of shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.59,0:25:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要好好记住这样子\N{\rEng}Remember what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.89,0:25:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们行差踏错…\N{\rEng}You fuck up in a firefight and I guarantee you a trip out of the bush...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证你们不能活着离开\N{\rEng}...in a body bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.73,0:25:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 混球 要提起精神\N{\rEng}Out here, assholes, you keep your shit wired tight at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.94,0:25:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 猪脑\N{\rEng}That goes for you, shit-for-brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.58,0:25:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能在埋伏时睡着\N{\rEng}You don't sleep on no fucking ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.22,0:25:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下次让我见到有人在埋伏时睡觉\N{\rEng}The next son of a bitch I catch copping Z's in the bush...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.79,0:25:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定不会放过他\N{\rEng}...I'm personally gonna make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是很认真的\N{\rEng}I shit you not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.26,0:25:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,将他入袋\N{\rEng}Tag him and bag him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.63,0:25:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有睡着\N{\rEng}I didn't fall asleep, sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.44,0:25:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是乔利亚 住口 鸟大便\N{\rEng}-It was Junior. -Shut up, chickenshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.70,0:25:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有麻烦了\N{\rEng}You're in big trouble, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.74,0:25:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,藉口像是屁眼 每个人都有一个\N{\rEng}Excuses are like assholes. Everybody's got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.94,0:25:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,别再胡闹\N{\rEng}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.75,0:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有两个队友需要照料\N{\rEng}We got two men need attention here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.85,0:26:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好军火和手榴弹\N{\rEng}Police up your extra ammo and frags.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.62,0:26:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要留任何东西给越南人\N{\rEng}Don't leave nothing for the dinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.89,0:26:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,背起嘉勒\N{\rEng}Carry Gardner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.83,0:26:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,若有多几天去学习 他不会死的\N{\rEng}Man would be alive if he had a few more days to learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.70,0:26:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒\N{\rEng}Hey, Taylor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\rEng}What's in the breeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.17,0:26:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,三天轻松任务\N{\rEng}Got light duty. Three days' worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜我们在基地营\N{\rEng}No shit. Too bad we're in base camp anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.77,0:26:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿着什么 啤酒么\N{\rEng}What you got? Beers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.21,0:27:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,从长官那里拿的 他偷我们的物资\N{\rEng}Stole some from the Top's supply. Shit, he's been stealing it from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.28,0:27:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你回来了么\N{\rEng}What are you, back?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.01,0:27:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是了\N{\rEng}Yeah, it looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里拿到的啤酒\N{\rEng}Where'd you get the beers, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.62,0:27:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到的\N{\rEng}I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.82,0:27:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,找到么 我会告发你\N{\rEng}Found it? You're going on report, son, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.69,0:27:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们跟我来 有工作给你们\N{\rEng}Both of you, come with me. I got a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.97,0:27:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.54,0:27:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不适合做这个\N{\rEng}I'm too short for this shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.78,0:27:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是在玩弄我们\N{\rEng}They're always fucking with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.98,0:27:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有停止过\N{\rEng}No letup.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.91,0:27:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是政治\N{\rEng}Politics, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.95,0:27:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的政治\N{\rEng}Fucking politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.75,0:27:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尼尔拍长官的马屁 拍的都快成马屁精了\N{\rEng}That O'Neill's got his nose so far up Top's ass, he's gotta be Pinocchio.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.76,0:27:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,39天之后\N{\rEng}Thirty-nine and a wake-up.
