Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.45,0:54:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉说烧掉这里 听到了吗\N{\rEng}Captain says to torch this place, hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.12,0:55:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,烧掉这里\N{\rEng}Torch this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.76,0:55:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,烧掉武器\N{\rEng}Blow the weapons in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.66,0:55:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,集合他们 我们时间不多\N{\rEng}Round up suspected VC and shake it up! We ain't got much light left!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.73,0:55:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 你为什么不作出行动\N{\rEng}Lieutenant, why the fuck didn't you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.20,0:55:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么\N{\rEng}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.10,0:55:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在说什么\N{\rEng}You know what the fuck I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.84,0:55:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不知道 我不知道你他妈的在说什么\N{\rEng}No, I don't. I don't know what the fuck you're talking about, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.91,0:55:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快点出发 快 听到命令了吧\N{\rEng}Move it out! Let's go! You heard the lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.75,0:55:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 走了 妈的 烧掉武器 然后离开\N{\rEng}Taylor, let's go, for chrissake! Police up the weapons and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.32,0:55:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛 来吧\N{\rEng}Come on, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.36,0:56:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,准备爆炸\N{\rEng}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.10,0:56:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,准备爆炸\N{\rEng}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.82,0:57:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.29,0:57:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 滚开\N{\rEng}You fucker! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.19,0:57:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开…不要那样做\N{\rEng}Get the fuck off! Don't do it! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.19,0:57:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 这是什么一回事\N{\rEng}You fucker! What is this, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.87,0:57:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你是同志吗\N{\rEng}You a homosexual?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.23,0:57:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 她是越南人\N{\rEng}What's your problem? She's a fucking dink.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.00,0:57:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她是人类 去你的\N{\rEng}She's a fucking human being, man! Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.97,0:57:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你这个可恶的新兵\N{\rEng}Total fucking cherry, Taylor!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.34,0:57:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的禽兽 你们全部都是禽兽\N{\rEng}Fucking animal! All of you! You're fucking animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.15,0:57:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Fucking lame fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.28,0:57:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你不属于越南 这里不适合你\N{\rEng}You don't belong in the Nam. This ain't your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一点都不明白吧\N{\rEng}You don't fucking get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.76,0:57:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不明白\N{\rEng}You just don't fucking get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.86,0:57:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\rEng}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.06,0:57:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,离开吧\N{\rEng}Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.00,0:58:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧\N{\rEng}Police up your dicks and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.30,0:59:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都看不见 我看到\N{\rEng}-I didn't see anything, sir. -I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.47,0:59:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士说那个是北越兵\N{\rEng}Sergeant Barnes reported the dink as NVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.30,0:59:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我的报告中 沃夫上尉是目击证人\N{\rEng}My report will have Lieutenant Wolfe as being witness to the shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.27,0:59:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 好\N{\rEng}All right, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.61,0:59:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中士 是\N{\rEng}-Staff Sergeant Barnes. -Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.31,0:59:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到总部后我要详细报告\N{\rEng}I want a full report from you when we get back to the CP.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.65,0:59:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你有日志 我有很多目击证人\N{\rEng}You got a diary. I have plenty of eyewitnesses, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.98,0:59:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是现在\N{\rEng}Not now, goddamn it! Not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.59,0:59:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回到总部才调查这件事\N{\rEng}We'll get into this at the base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.92,0:59:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证如果发现非法杀戮…\N{\rEng}I can promise you, if I find out there was an illegal killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.53,0:59:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会有军事法庭\N{\rEng}...there will be a court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.56,0:59:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我要全军作战 你们别再吵\N{\rEng}Right now, I need every man in the field, and you two will cease fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.03,0:59:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩和伊利亚中士 听到吗\N{\rEng}Staff Sergeant Barnes. Sergeant Elias. You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.44,0:59:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是 知道\N{\rEng}-Yes, sir. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.64,0:59:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你们从东面再去那越共地堡\N{\rEng}We're going back into that NVA bunker tomorrow, this time from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.14,0:59:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们休息一下 晚上七点钟回来开会\N{\rEng}You people get some rest, and be back here at the CP at 1 900 for a briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.05,0:59:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是\N{\rEng}-Yes, sir. -Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.39,1:00:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们会在乎我们吗\N{\rEng}Come on, man! You think these chucks give a fuck about you and me?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.63,1:00:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛 也许会是你阻碍了巴恩\N{\rEng}It could have been you, Harold, you got in Barnes' way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.50,1:00:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那个宾尼呢\N{\rEng}And that Bunny?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.53,1:00:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个疯子\N{\rEng}That motherfucker's crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.87,1:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他令我不寒而栗\N{\rEng}I mean, he scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.04,1:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他很可怕\N{\rEng}He just scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.34,1:00:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经受牵连\N{\rEng}You bloods are getting too hung up on this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.58,1:00:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这些越南人比你想像中聪明\N{\rEng}These gooks are a lot smarter than you think.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.41,1:00:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩知道他在做什么\N{\rEng}You know, Barnes knows his shit, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是北越兵\N{\rEng}They was NVA, every last of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.39,1:00:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他带领我们走到这里了 他会带领我们走完这场战争\N{\rEng}He got us this far. He'll get us the rest of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.49,1:00:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.32,1:00:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,基督教徒不会到处杀人\N{\rEng}A Christian don't go around a village, cutting off heads and shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.43,1:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,情况失去控制了 完全失控了\N{\rEng}This shit is really getting out of hand, blowing out of control.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.23,1:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你不知道怎样分别…\N{\rEng}Seems to me that you don't seem to know the difference...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.40,1:00:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,事情的轻重\N{\rEng}...the way you always shoot up that shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.70,1:00:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道…\N{\rEng}I don't know, brothers...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.04,1:00:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但我内心大受伤害\N{\rEng}...but I'm hurting real bad inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.95,1:00:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 伊利亚不能证明什么\N{\rEng}Don't worry, sarge. Elias won't be able to prove a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.35,1:01:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个麻烦制造者\N{\rEng}He's a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.65,1:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚像华盛顿的政客…\N{\rEng}Elias is a water walker. Like them politicians in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.55,1:01:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想独力打这场仗\N{\rEng}...trying to fight this war with one hand tied around their balls.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.76,1:01:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有时间进行审讯\N{\rEng}Ain't no need or time for a courtroom out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.23,1:01:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 谢谢你\N{\rEng}-Sarge. -Thanks, Bun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.93,1:01:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样\N{\rEng}How did it go there, Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.10,1:01:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可恶的伊利亚\N{\rEng}Yeah, thataway, sarge! Fucking Elias, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.94,1:01:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个卑鄙小人\N{\rEng}He's a fucking rat, that's what he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.24,1:01:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他会连累这个连的所有人\N{\rEng}He'll get everybody in this platoon in deep shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.48,1:01:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人要教训他\N{\rEng}Somebody ought to frag his ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.05,1:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为呢 会有调查吗\N{\rEng}So, what do you think? Gonna be an investigation or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.15,1:01:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,鲍布\N{\rEng}Bob?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.56,1:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你太担心了 中士会解决他\N{\rEng}O'Neill, you worry too much. Sarge will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.83,1:01:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚天色很美\N{\rEng}It's a beautiful night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.57,1:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这里的夜晚\N{\rEng}Yeah, I love this place at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.91,1:01:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,繁星…\N{\rEng}The stars....
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.04,1:02:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它们没有对与错 它们就是在那里\N{\rEng}There's no right or wrong in them. They're just there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.92,1:02:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的比喻很好\N{\rEng}That's a nice way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.86,1:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩憎恨你吧\N{\rEng}Barnes has it in for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.36,1:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩相信他所做的一切\N{\rEng}Barnes believes in what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.13,1:02:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 你相信吗\N{\rEng}And you? Do you believe?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.80,1:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,1965年时吗 我会相信\N{\rEng}In '65? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.31,1:02:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在呢\N{\rEng}Now?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.24,1:02:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不相信\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.68,1:02:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,今天所发生的事只是开始\N{\rEng}What happened today is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.88,1:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会输掉这场仗\N{\rEng}We're gonna lose this war.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.49,1:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.29,1:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为我们会输\N{\rEng}You really think so? Us?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.86,1:02:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们欺负别人太久了\N{\rEng}We've been kicking other people's asses for so long...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.86,1:02:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在轮到我们被打击\N{\rEng}...I figure it's time we got ours kicked.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.84,1:03:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在挣扎\N{\rEng}Day by day, I struggle to maintain...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.48,1:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我努力维持体力和意志\N{\rEng}...not only my strength, but my sanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.38,1:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很模糊\N{\rEng}It"s all a blur.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.25,1:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有气力写信\N{\rEng}I have no energy to write.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.65,1:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能分辨对与错\N{\rEng}I don"t know what"s right or wrong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.74,1:03:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的士气低落 出现内讧\N{\rEng}The morale of the men is low. A civil war in the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.61,1:03:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一半支持伊利亚 一半支持巴恩\N{\rEng}Half the men with Elias, half with Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.02,1:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多猜忌和憎恨\N{\rEng}There"s a lot of suspicion and hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.52,1:03:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们竟然在自相残杀\N{\rEng}I can"t believe we"re fighting each other instead of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.46,1:03:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,数着日子和留意着周围 没别的\N{\rEng}Counting days and the six inches in front of my face. Not much else.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.60,1:03:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母 希望你一切安好\N{\rEng}Hope things are well, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.90,1:03:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉妈妈和爸爸…\N{\rEng}Tell Mom and Dad I--
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.20,1:03:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道告诉他们什么的 柯里斯上\N{\rEng}Well, just tell them. Chris.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.06,1:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你以为会被派去洗衣服\N{\rEng}Hey, big boy. I know you thought you had that laundry gig all laid out.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.83,1:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把自己涂白 才能得到那些工作\N{\rEng}Hell, I gotta paint myself white just to get one of those jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.50,1:04:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我递了申请去割包皮 我要离开\N{\rEng}Got my request in for a circumcision. I'm getting my big ass out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.77,1:04:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你会成为犹太教教士吗\N{\rEng}What are you gonna do, become a rabbi?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.08,1:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,水蛭\N{\rEng}Leech.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.78,1:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,继续走\N{\rEng}All right! Move it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.19,1:04:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喝 你会得痢疾的\N{\rEng}Don't drink that, asshole. You're gonna get malaria.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.96,1:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望会\N{\rEng}Yeah, I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.86,1:04:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.07,1:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 莱纳被击中\N{\rEng}Doc! Up here! Lerner's hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.44,1:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 华伦被击中\N{\rEng}Sergeant, Warren's hit!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.08,1:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事 他们有火箭榴弹\N{\rEng}-What's going on? -They got RPGs, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.28,1:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已在这里埋伏了很久\N{\rEng}It's an ambush! They were just waiting for us here!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.28,1:05:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁负责防守 莱纳和华伦\N{\rEng}-Who's on point? -Lerner and Warren.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.59,1:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里\N{\rEng}Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.99,1:05:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 混球 派火力上前\N{\rEng}Goddamn it, you assholes! Get some firepower up there!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.06,1:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEng}Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.54,1:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 火箭\N{\rEng}Watch out! Rockets!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.58,1:06:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,莱纳在哪里\N{\rEng}Where the fuck is Lerner?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.59,1:06:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他在木头那边\N{\rEng}He's over there! By the log!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.44,1:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,开火坐标649602\N{\rEng}Fire mission. Grid: 6-4-9-4-0-2.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.82,1:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,方向610\N{\rEng}Direction: 6-1 -0--
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.25,1:06:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,调整发射 完毕\N{\rEng}Adjust fire. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.92,1:06:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 他们会步步进逼\N{\rEng}Lieutenant, they'll get in tight under the arty!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.26,1:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到缺口 让我带人去那边\N{\rEng}I saw a cut. Let me take some men and roll up that flank.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.36,1:07:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,叫巴恩去 我们已有四个人受伤 你要我怎么办\N{\rEng}Get Barnes! Elias, we got four down. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.27,1:07:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,红连在哪里 叫那些混蛋赶来\N{\rEng}Where the fuck is Red Platoon?! Tell those assholes to get up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.07,1:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 你在这里做什么\N{\rEng}Elias, what are you doing back here?
