Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.59,1:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去吧\N{\rEng}You got them! Take off!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.80,1:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,继续掩护我们\N{\rEng}You keep pouring off that cover fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.67,1:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想在外面孤军作战\N{\rEng}I don't want to be stuck out there with my ass hanging in the breeze.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.77,1:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚 不要教我怎么打仗\N{\rEng}You don't tell me how to run my war, Elias.
