Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.41,1:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里你属于我 快行动\N{\rEng}Out here you belong to me! Now, move!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.68,1:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩 你是个混蛋\N{\rEng}You're an asshole, Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.48,1:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,叫奥尼尔上前来\N{\rEng}Get that asshole O'Neill up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.05,1:08:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶\N{\rEng}Holy fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.13,1:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,伏下\N{\rEng}Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.81,1:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹…\N{\rEng}Ammo! Ammo!
