Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.26,1:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋\N{\rEng}Fucking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.38,1:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出来\N{\rEng}Get it out!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.62,1:09:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,军医\N{\rEng}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.47,1:09:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,有地雷\N{\rEng}Satchel charge!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.94,1:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,军医\N{\rEng}Doc!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.34,1:09:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 过来帮我 好\N{\rEng}-Doc, help me out. -All right, down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.01,1:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,天\N{\rEng}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.82,1:10:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 不要留下我\N{\rEng}-You okay? -Don't leave me, man.
