Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.29,1:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的 不要留下我\N{\rEng}-Hey, Gator, you'll be okay, man. -Don't leave me, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.76,1:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\rEng}Gator? Gator, you'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.09,1:10:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,放开他\N{\rEng}Let him go, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.30,1:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,别吵 泰勒 你跟我们来\N{\rEng}-Drop your rucks. -Taylor, you're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.63,1:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,求你不要走\N{\rEng}Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.20,1:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的\N{\rEng}You're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.91,1:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.11,1:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 照顾他\N{\rEng}Doc, take care of him, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.98,1:10:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,炮手 B2实际射程\N{\rEng}Redleg, Redleg. Ripper Bravo 2 actual.
