Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.69,1:10:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个自大混蛋\N{\rEng}You ignorant asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.79,1:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你给他们什么座标\N{\rEng}What the fuck coordinates are you giving?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.26,1:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你的座标已经令很多人受伤\N{\rEng}You wasted a lot of people up there with your fucked-up fire mission!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.26,1:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗\N{\rEng}Do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.90,1:10:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 妈的\N{\rEng}Do you know that? Ah, shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.40,1:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,炮手 这是B2\N{\rEng}Redleg! Redleg! Ripper Bravo 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.50,1:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,停火…\N{\rEng}Check your fire! Check your fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.42,1:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\rEng}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.82,1:11:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,坚守这里 枪杀任何走动着的东西\N{\rEng}Stagger yourself across this line. Shoot anything that moves.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.63,1:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会从那里过来\N{\rEng}They'll be coming from over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.66,1:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只要被他们攻破 我们便死定了\N{\rEng}Any one of them gets through, we are truly fucked.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.53,1:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里\N{\rEng}Where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.70,1:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到下游大约一百米处…\N{\rEng}Down by the river about 1 00 meters...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.11,1:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以防他们准备从外围进攻\N{\rEng}...in case they try to flank us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.94,1:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,第三连正在后面赶来\N{\rEng}3rd Platoon is coming behind us. Watch for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.08,1:11:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以和你一起去吗\N{\rEng}Hey. Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.51,1:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我单独行事比较敏捷\N{\rEng}No. I move faster alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.33,1:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,让炮兵队来处理\N{\rEng}Let's let arty do a bit of the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.80,1:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,叫所有人去教堂…\N{\rEng}Tell everyone to pull back to the church...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.93,1:12:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,和第三连会合 知道吗\N{\rEng}...and link up with 3rd Platoon. You got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.77,1:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚怎么样 他会孤立无援\N{\rEng}What about Elias? If we pull back, he'll be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.01,1:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 你也快去\N{\rEng}You just haul ass too, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.88,1:12:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找他\N{\rEng}I'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.77,1:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.75,1:12:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我击中两个 我击中一个\N{\rEng}-I got two of them fuckers, man. -I got one.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.89,1:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,打倒胡志明\N{\rEng}Ho Chi Minh sucks dead dick!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.69,1:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,克罗福\N{\rEng}Crawford!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.63,1:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\rEng}Oh, man. Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.96,1:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 我从没想过会被击中的\N{\rEng}Kiss my ass. Man, I never thought I'd get hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.60,1:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你击中两个混蛋\N{\rEng}A lung, babe. You got two of them fuckers.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.47,1:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚在哪里 一班越兵刚经过\N{\rEng}Where's Elias? A bunch of gooks came through here.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.27,1:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们击中三个 对\N{\rEng}-We got three of them fuckers. -Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.41,1:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,炮兵队调动了 我们要撤退\N{\rEng}The arty shifted. We're pulling back.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.78,1:13:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,扶伤者去教堂\N{\rEng}Get your wounded man and get the fuck back to church.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.91,1:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚在外面 我会去找他\N{\rEng}-Elias is still out there. -I'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.08,1:13:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在我送你去军法审判之前 快扶克罗福进去 快\N{\rEng}Get Crawford in now before I article 15 both your asses. Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.96,1:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.61,1:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快到达了 快\N{\rEng}Almost there, brother. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.01,1:15:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 你在哪里\N{\rEng}Medic, where the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.71,1:15:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快会没事\N{\rEng}It's gonna be all right in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.05,1:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 你去哪里\N{\rEng}Taylor, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.64,1:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚死了\N{\rEng}Elias is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.65,1:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,和他们一起撤退\N{\rEng}Fall back with the platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.75,1:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.98,1:16:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\rEng}He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.75,1:16:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对 他在一百米外\N{\rEng}Yeah, he's back there about 1 00 meters.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.42,1:17:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到他吗 哪里\N{\rEng}You saw him? Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.52,1:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了 到处都是越军 快走\N{\rEng}He's dead! There's gooks all over the goddamn place! Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.98,1:17:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Let's go! Come on, move it!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.98,1:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 快 快走\N{\rEng}Let's go! Move it! Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.24,1:18:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哈洛 你没事吧 下一个轮到你\N{\rEng}You okay, Harold? You're on the next one! You're okay, bud!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.99,1:19:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.33,1:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他们抓到伊利亚\N{\rEng}They've got Elias!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.00,1:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.07,1:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,退后…\N{\rEng}Back down! Back down there!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.45,1:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蛇1-9队 飞行4 下面仍然有一个士兵\N{\rEng}Snake 1-9, Fly 4. There"s still one of the men down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.50,1:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,停火…\N{\rEng}Hold your arms. Guns, hold off.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.39,1:21:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀死他\N{\rEng}He killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.39,1:21:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道是他 我看到他的眼神\N{\rEng}I know he did. I saw his eyes when he came in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.93,1:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道不是越兵 你没有证据\N{\rEng}How do you know the dinks didn't get him? You got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.57,1:21:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,证据就在他的眼神 我看得出\N{\rEng}Proof's in the eyes. When you know, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.20,1:21:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看见 我知道你在想什么\N{\rEng}You saw. I know what you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.60,1:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天解决他\N{\rEng}I say we frag him tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.47,1:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我赞成 以牙还牙\N{\rEng}I go with that. An eye for an eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.44,1:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让军事法庭处理吧\N{\rEng}I say let military justice do the job on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.91,1:21:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的军事法庭 你在说笑吗\N{\rEng}Come on, fuck the military justice! Are you joking me?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.75,1:21:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会相信谁 奥尼尔 宾尼 全是胡说\N{\rEng}Whose story you think they'll believe? O'Neill's? Bunny's? Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.09,1:21:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩不会放过你的\N{\rEng}You try that, Barnes will shove it back up your ass, with a candle on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.49,1:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我们应该怎么做\N{\rEng}What do you suggest we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.49,1:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们小心 巴恩会一个个的解决他们\N{\rEng}Watch your own asses. Barnes will be coming down on all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.83,1:21:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们忘记和伊利亚的美好日子吗\N{\rEng}You gonna forget about Elias? All the good times we had here?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.34,1:21:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你想把头砍下来治头痛\N{\rEng}Shit, you trying to cure the headache by cutting off the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.67,1:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚没有叫你为他打仗\N{\rEng}Elias didn't ask you to fight his battles for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.51,1:22:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真的有天堂 天啊 我希望真的有\N{\rEng}And if there's a heaven, and God, I hope there is...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.41,1:22:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他会在上面喝到大醉\N{\rEng}...he's sitting up there drunk as a fucking monkey and smoking shit...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.12,1:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他把痛苦留在这里\N{\rEng}...because he left his pains down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.39,1:22:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你错了 总之巴恩是杀人凶手\N{\rEng}You're wrong! Anyway you cut it, Barnes is a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.96,1:22:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对 泰勒…\N{\rEng}-Right on. -Taylor...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.03,1:22:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你当初入伍时说很欣赏巴恩\N{\rEng}...when you first came in here, you told me how you admired the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.77,1:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我错了 你做任何事都是错的\N{\rEng}-I was wrong. -You've never been right about nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.17,1:22:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这班混蛋 留心听着\N{\rEng}Dig this, you assholes, and dig it good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.88,1:22:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩中枪七次都没有死去\N{\rEng}Barnes been shot seven times, and he ain't dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.05,1:22:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那对你有意思吗\N{\rEng}Does that mean anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.88,1:22:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩是不会死的\N{\rEng}Barnes ain't meant to die.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.05,1:22:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一能杀死他的是他自己\N{\rEng}The only thing that can kill Barnes is Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.26,1:22:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在谈死亡吗\N{\rEng}Talking about killing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.60,1:23:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是专家吗\N{\rEng}You all experts?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.54,1:23:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都知道杀戮吗\N{\rEng}You all know about killing?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.71,1:23:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听听 猪头\N{\rEng}Well, I'd like to hear about it, potheads.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.52,1:23:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你们抽这个来逃避现实\N{\rEng}You smoke this shit to escape from reality?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.46,1:23:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要这个\N{\rEng}Me, I don't need this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.00,1:23:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是现实\N{\rEng}I am reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.24,1:23:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现实应该是这样 而现实就是这样\N{\rEng}There's the way it ought to be, and there's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.98,1:23:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚满口一派胡言\N{\rEng}Elias was full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.65,1:23:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚是个斗士\N{\rEng}Elias was a crusader.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.13,1:24:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会跟听从命令的人作对\N{\rEng}Now, I got no fight with any man who does what he's told.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.66,1:24:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但当他不听命时…\N{\rEng}But when he don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.40,1:24:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,运作便会崩溃\N{\rEng}...the machine breaks down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.10,1:24:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,运作崩溃时 我们就会崩溃\N{\rEng}And when the machine breaks down, we break down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.51,1:24:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会许容那样的事\N{\rEng}I ain't going to allow that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.14,1:24:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们任何一个都不能\N{\rEng}From any of you.
