Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.84,1:35:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,乔利亚 我们所做的一切\N{\rEng}You know, Junior? Some of the things we done, man...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.85,1:35:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得我们在做错事\N{\rEng}...I don't feel like we done something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.82,1:35:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时…\N{\rEng}But sometimes, man...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.49,1:35:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我有不祥的感觉\N{\rEng}...I get this bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.59,1:35:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我坦然对随军牧师说我喜欢这里\N{\rEng}I told the padre the truth. I like it here.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.13,1:35:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以为所欲为 没有人理会你\N{\rEng}You get to do what you want, nobody fucks with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.30,1:35:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你只用担心死亡\N{\rEng}The only worry you got is dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.07,1:35:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,反正死的时候你不会知道\N{\rEng}And if that happens, you won't know about it...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.64,1:35:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那么担心什么\N{\rEng}...so, what the fuck, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.91,1:35:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要和你同一个坑么\N{\rEng}Shit. I got to be in this hole with you, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.68,1:35:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我早知道我不应该来\N{\rEng}I just know I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.21,1:36:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 你和爱迪墨菲在一起\N{\rEng}Don't you worry, Junior. You're hanging with Audie Murphy here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.69,1:36:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B3 B6 给我座标… 完毕\N{\rEng}Bravo 3, Bravo 6. Send me a grid, send me a grid. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.36,1:36:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 我们被困住了 他们在树丛里\N{\rEng}I can"t, sir. We"re pinned down. They"re in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.53,1:36:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好 3A 冷静下来 我会立即派人去轰炸\N{\rEng}Okay, 3 Alpha, now calm down, son. I'll get you a fire mission ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.56,1:36:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,先会发放烟雾 中尉和电讯兵已经死了\N{\rEng}-Smoke will be first. -Lieutenant and radioman are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.03,1:36:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到地图\N{\rEng}I can"t find the map.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.40,1:36:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们分布在四周 好几百个 我听到他们说越南话\N{\rEng}They"re all around us. Hundreds of them. I can hear them talking gook.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.94,1:36:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,3A 看着烟雾 告诉我要转向哪里\N{\rEng}3 Alpha, spot that smoke and tell me where to shift.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.01,1:36:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静下来 撑着点 我们会救你\N{\rEng}Just calm down. Hang in there. We'll get you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.88,1:36:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里被袭 完毕\N{\rEng}Where did the rounds hit? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.20,1:36:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,3A6 你可以调整 开火位置吗 完毕\N{\rEng}3 Alpha 6, how about those rounds? Can you adjust fire? Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.27,1:37:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,3A6 如果你不能说话 按键两次 完毕\N{\rEng}3 Alpha 6, if you can't talk, just key your handset twice. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.76,1:37:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\rEng}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.87,1:38:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,罗德里的坑被击中\N{\rEng}Trip flare, Rodriguez's hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.55,1:38:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭榴弹\N{\rEng}RPG.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.99,1:38:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 法兰西 这里\N{\rEng}-Taylor. Francis. -Over here, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.72,1:38:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事 罗德里的坑被炸\N{\rEng}What's going on? Rodriguez's hole just got nailed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.46,1:38:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来了 附近满布越南兵\N{\rEng}Here it is. We got gooks in the fucking perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.36,1:38:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,完了…\N{\rEng}Shit. That's it!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.56,1:38:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打败了A连\N{\rEng}They got through Alpha Company. Anything that don't identify itself...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.64,1:38:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,向任何不明物体开枪\N{\rEng}...fucking blow it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.54,1:38:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 空军正在赶来 他们会拼命投弹的\N{\rEng}Fuck. Air strikes coming in. They'll be laying snake and nape.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.74,1:38:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要离开散兵坑\N{\rEng}Don't get out of your fucking holes. Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.01,1:38:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了\N{\rEng}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.18,1:38:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在侦察我们\N{\rEng}They're probing us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.49,1:38:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不惜一切地攻入\N{\rEng}They'll go up and down, trying to get through.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.12,1:38:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,留在这里 冷静点 我很快回来\N{\rEng}All right, stay here. Stay cool. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.29,1:39:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,F队 回音 威士忌 完毕\N{\rEng}Foxtrot, Foxtrot. Echo. Whiskey. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.68,1:39:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁\N{\rEng}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.22,1:39:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪\N{\rEng}Don't shoot! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.09,1:39:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是埋伏 这边\N{\rEng}It's the ambush. Over here, man, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:37.86,1:39:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 水\N{\rEng}-Shit. -Water!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.33,1:39:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到处都是 正走向这里\N{\rEng}They're all over the place! Hundreds of them! Moving this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.67,1:39:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他们击溃我们 我们没有还击机会\N{\rEng}They wiped us out! We didn't have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.21,1:39:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,总部在哪里 后面\N{\rEng}-Where's the CP? -Back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.14,1:39:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开 他们不会停止的\N{\rEng}Get out of here! They're on my ass! They ain't stopping for shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.88,1:39:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 我们走吧\N{\rEng}Hey, Taylor, let's di di.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.52,1:39:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你走\N{\rEng}You go.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.06,1:40:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\rEng}There.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.00,1:40:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,停火…\N{\rEng}No, hold it. Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.12,1:41:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开\N{\rEng}Out of the hole! Fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.82,1:41:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快离开壕沟 他们想炸掉兵坑\N{\rEng}Get out of the foxhole! They're gonna blow it!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.79,1:41:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧…\N{\rEng}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.99,1:41:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快点走 快 他们要炸掉…\N{\rEng}Fuck's sake. Move your fucking ass! They're gonna blow--
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.25,1:41:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怕\N{\rEng}Fuck me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.52,1:41:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\rEng}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.60,1:41:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 死吧\N{\rEng}Die, you motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.38,1:42:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮\N{\rEng}It's fucking beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.35,1:42:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么 你去哪里\N{\rEng}What are you doing? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.40,1:42:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Come on, motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.30,1:42:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能做得更好\N{\rEng}You can do better than that!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.77,1:42:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不断进攻\N{\rEng}They just keep coming, man! Fuck this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.11,1:42:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,回来 你这个懦夫\N{\rEng}Get back here, you gutless shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.41,1:43:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我B连\N{\rEng}Get me Bravo ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.74,1:43:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,C连报告三个坑失守 需要增援\N{\rEng}Charlie Company reports hand-to-hand, three holes are down. They need help.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.68,1:43:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,立即派A连的两个小组前去 快\N{\rEng}Okay, get two squads from Alpha down there right away. Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.21,1:43:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,空袭在哪里\N{\rEng}Where's that goddamn air strike?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.45,1:43:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去哪里\N{\rEng}Hey, you two! Where the fuck are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.21,1:44:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,联络不到任何人吗\N{\rEng}Can't you get anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.57,1:44:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 联络不到巴恩他们\N{\rEng}Negative contact. Can't raise Barnes, 2 Bravo, 2 Charlie, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.14,1:44:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给我联络总部 总部\N{\rEng}-Get me 6! -Bravo 6!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.28,1:44:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,柏加被击中 拉他进来\N{\rEng}-Parker's hit! -Get him in!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.69,1:44:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正在攻入\N{\rEng}They're coming through our line!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.99,1:44:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩在哪里 他死了 他们全都死了\N{\rEng}-Where's Barnes?! -He's dead! They're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.26,1:44:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,六队 中尉\N{\rEng}Six, L.T.!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.16,1:44:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 我们被袭击 我们会撤退\N{\rEng}Captain, we've been overrun. We're pulling back. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.63,1:44:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 撤退到哪里 到处都是他们\N{\rEng}Goddamn it! Where will you pull back to? They're all over the perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.41,1:44:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你听着 你们要坚守作战\N{\rEng}Now you be advised! You will hold in place and you will fight!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.71,1:44:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 即是指你 六队通话完毕\N{\rEng}That means you, lieutenant. Bravo 6 out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.54,1:45:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这里被袭\N{\rEng}We got zips in the wire down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.91,1:45:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 B6 但我们不能再接近了\N{\rEng}Roger that, Bravo 6. Can"t run it any closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.12,1:45:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们准备投弹 我们燃料充足\N{\rEng}We"re packing snake and nape but we"re bingo on fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.39,1:45:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的决定 投下所有炸弹\N{\rEng}For the record, it's my call! Dump all you've got on my pos.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.19,1:45:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说投下所有炸弹\N{\rEng}I say again, expend all remaining in my perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.93,1:45:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一场很棒的战争 B6通话完毕\N{\rEng}It's a lovely fucking war. Bravo 6 out.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.23,1:45:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 这是你的决定\N{\rEng}Roger your last, Bravo 6. We copy it"s your call.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.67,1:45:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他们留守散兵坑 你们支持着\N{\rEng}Get them in their holes. Hang tough, Bravo 6.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.94,1:45:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会从树顶投下炸弹\N{\rEng}We are coming cocked for treetops.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.47,1:46:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩\N{\rEng}Barnes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.44,1:46:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.62,1:49:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给我找军医\N{\rEng}Get me a medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.95,1:49:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快去\N{\rEng}Go on, boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:46.44,1:49:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下手吧\N{\rEng}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.64,1:50:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 三点钟位置还有越兵活着\N{\rEng}Look out, we got live gooks at 3:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.18,1:50:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\rEng}Come on, Elmo! Move your flea-bitten ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.92,1:50:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\rEng}You okay? You all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.72,1:50:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你能走动吗\N{\rEng}Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.69,1:50:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里需要军医\N{\rEng}Hey, doc! We need a medic up here!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.23,1:50:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 这里有伤兵\N{\rEng}-Come on, Elmo. -Doc, we got wounded here!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.49,1:51:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,战争一定是很激烈\N{\rEng}That must have been some fucking fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.32,1:51:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你一个吗\N{\rEng}You alone here, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.96,1:51:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.99,1:51:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那些混球 他们留下我\N{\rEng}Bunch of fucking faggots. They all left me.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.65,1:52:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,122个受伤 仍在点算中\N{\rEng}1 22 wounded and still counting.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.62,1:52:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,估计有五百个伤者…\N{\rEng}Estimate 500...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.05,1:52:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军22人阵亡 仍在点算中 完毕\N{\rEng}...Victor Charlie K.I.A. 22 and still counting. Over.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.76,1:52:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒 是你吗\N{\rEng}Taylor! That you?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:25.60,1:52:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰西\N{\rEng}Hey, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.80,1:52:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 我还好 你好吗\N{\rEng}-Hey, man, how you doing? -I'm okay. How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.04,1:52:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\N{\rEng}Fine, man. Just fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:31.40,1:52:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受过两次伤可以离开这里\N{\rEng}Hey, dig it, we two-timers. We're gonna get out of here, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:34.97,1:52:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在医院再见\N{\rEng}I'm gonna see you in the hospital. We gonna get high, high. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.22,1:52:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 我没事\N{\rEng}-How you doing? -I'm just fine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.38,1:52:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好 因为第二连由你指挥\N{\rEng}Good, because you got 2nd Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.99,1:52:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\rEng}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.23,1:53:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好吗 准备好\N{\rEng}-Ready? -You bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:30.36,1:54:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,现在回想一切…\N{\rEng}I think now, looking back...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.09,1:54:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是对抗敌人 而是自己\N{\rEng}...we did not fight the enemy, we fought ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.16,1:54:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人就在我们心中\N{\rEng}...and the enemy was in us.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:42.74,1:54:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,战争对我来说现在已经完结\N{\rEng}The war is over for me now...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.10,1:54:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但它永远会存留在我的心中里\N{\rEng}...but it will always be there the rest of my days.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.44,1:54:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伊利亚会和…\N{\rEng}As I"m sure Elias will be...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.84,1:54:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,巴恩为了 像罗德所说的 “灵魂的掌控”继续作战\N{\rEng}...fighting with Barnes for, what Rhah called, possession of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:57.75,1:54:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时会觉得…\N{\rEng}There are times since...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.52,1:55:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那两个父亲的儿子\N{\rEng}...I have felt like the child born of those two fathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.13,1:55:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但无论如何…\N{\rEng}But be that as it may...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.66,1:55:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有责任重建社会…\N{\rEng}... those of us who did make it have an obligation to build again.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.03,1:55:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,教导别人我们认识的一切…\N{\rEng}To teach to others what we know...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.57,1:55:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们利用剩下的一生…\N{\rEng}...and to try with what"s left of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.51,1:55:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试找寻生命的意义\N{\rEng}... to find a goodness and meaning to this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.62,1:55:40.79,Default,,0,0,15,,献给在越战中牺牲的士兵

